        protected void drawCircleData​(NMapCircleData circleData,
                              NMapCircleStyle defaultCircleStyle,
                              android.graphics.Canvas canvas,
                              NMapView mapView,
                              boolean isDrawnOnSnapshot,
                              boolean isDrawingOnSnapshot)
        Draw circle data.
        Parameters:
        circleData - circle data to be draw.
        defaultCircleStyle - default circle style.
        canvas - The Canvas upon which to draw. Note that this may already have a transformation applied, so be sure to leave it the way you found it.
        mapView - the NMapView that requested the draw. Use NMapView.getProjection() to convert between on-screen pixels and latitude/longitude pairs.
